name: Service Booking Summary
query:
SELECT
    name AS "Booking ID:Link/Service Booking:120",
    customer_name AS "Customer Name:Data:200",
    service_type AS "Service Type:Select:120",
    preferred_date_time AS "Preferred Date/Time:Datetime:180",
    workflow_state AS "Status:Select:100",
    creation AS "Created On:Datetime:160"
FROM
    `tabService Booking`
WHERE
    (service_type = %(service_type)s OR %(service_type)s IS NULL)
    AND (workflow_state = %(workflow_state)s OR %(workflow_state)s IS NULL)
ORDER BY
    creation DESC
